  "description": {
    "zh": "你好，小伙子，我真佩服你的机敏。当然，我不想你生病，健康是最重要的。我忘了提醒你要小心带来的血液样本，希望你没有什么裸露的伤口......还有别忘了洗手。话又说回来，谁知道这血样被风吹日晒多久了呢？无论如何，请务必注意身体，不然我们很可能在撤离完塔科夫民众和我们自己之前就倒下了……",
    "en": "Good day, young man. The degree of your deftness never ceases to leave me in admiration. Naturally, I wouldn’t want you to fall ill, so health before everything. I forgot to warn you that you have to be careful with the blood samples you brought. I hope you haven't cut yourself... and have washed your hands. Although, who knows how long it has been exposed to sun, wind, and whatnot. In any case, I would still advise you to pay attention to your health, otherwise, it all might end before we evacuate the people and ourselves from Tarkov."
  },
